  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Communicator
    Robot's communicator for sending and receiving information with PC Called on by the Robot
    Detector
    The Detector is responsible for identifying obstacles using the touch sensors Detector runs in its own thread so it is constantly able to identify objects and notify Robot
    Message
    class created for sending commands from commuicator to robot
    Robot
    Object that carries out primary tasks for robot including navigation Calls on Locator, Communicator and Navigator to complete tasks
    Scanner
    Uses the light sensor to identify the angle of both light sources by identifying the peaks of light intensity when rotating in both directions Uses the ultrasonic sensor to determine distance to nearest object at specific angle Called on by Locator for fixing position
    Tester
    Test file for Bomb Locator
